Place the avocado, onions, garlic, and Swanson(R) Chicken Broth in a food processor or blender. Process until smooth, 7 or 8 pulses. Transfer mixture to a bowl. Stir in yogurt, half-and-half, lemon juice, sriracha chili sauce, salt and pepper. Fold in the corn kernels. Cover and refrigerate until chilled, at least 2 hours. Ladle the soup into bowls. Garnish each serving with a single shrimp.